A suspected thug beaten to death on Friday and his body set ablaze at Sultan Hamud town in Makueni county.The man was found attempting to break into a kiosk at 6am.Police officers took the body to Makindu Level 4 Hospital mortuary.Last week, an unknown number of armed gangsters invaded the town and hacked two guards to death.They then broke into several shops and made away with gas cylinders.A third guard is still fighting for his life at the Kenyatta National Hospital, where he was admitted in critical condition. He suffered serious head wounds and it is suspected he was hacked with a panga.